00:45:46,875 --> 00:45:47,875
Sembilan puluh.

323
00:45:49,417 --> 00:45:50,625
Sembilan puluh satu.

324
00:45:52,208 --> 00:45:53,375
Sembilan puluh dua.

325
00:45:55,875 --> 00:45:56,917
Kau bisa.

326
00:45:57,583 --> 00:45:59,125
Sembilan puluh tiga.

327
00:45:59,750 --> 00:46:00,750
Bagus!

